Use that Spacewalk server to automatically (without touching it) install a new pair of OS instances, with 
which you will then create a Master/Master pair of LDAP servers. Make sure they register with the Spacewalk server. 
Do not allow anonymous bind, do not use unencrypted LDAP.


-How to set up an openLDAP server?

https://kifarunix.com/install-and-setup-openldap-on-centos-8/

-How to set up master/master pair of openLDAP servers?

https://kifarunix.com/setup-openldap-master-master-replication-on-centos-8/

-How to use Spacewalk server to automatically install a new pair of OS instances, which then you will create a master/master pair of
openLDAP server?

https://docs.oracle.com/en/operating-systems/spacewalk/2.7/admin/alt_vt3_z5.html

